(252, 'Meril Baby Olive Oil', 'meril-baby-olive-oil', '100 ml', 260, 270, 1, 3, 5, '1768286523-image-Meril Baby Olive Oil 100 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">The \"first crushed\" oil from the finest and freshest olives comes to you in Meril Baby Olive Oil for the delicate need of your child\'s skin. Since Meril Baby Olive Oil does not contain any paraffin, your child will not feel the discomfort of rashes and dryness. The skin tissues become healthier since their moisture balance is taken care of absolutely naturally! Meril Baby Olive Oil ensures that the soft, supple nature of your child\'s skin remains so. While you are giving your child a gentle massage, his/her bones will grow stronger and better with Meril Baby Olive Oil.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-07-30 18:23:08', '2026-01-13 17:42:03'),
