(266, 'Meril Baby Gel Orange Toothpaste', 'meril-baby-gel-orange-toothpaste', '45 gm', 95, 100, 1, 5, 5, '1768374743-image-Meril Baby Gel Orange Toothpaste 45 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Baby\'s teeth and gums are incredibly soft and delicate, requiring gentle care. It is important to avoid using adult toothpaste, as its strong ingredients can potentially harm rather than benefit your baby. Therefore, it is not advisable to use such products for your little one. Instead, Meril Baby Gel Toothpaste offers a specially formulated solution that ensures the gentle care your baby\'s milk teeth and gums need. Here are the key features of Meril Baby Gel Toothpaste:</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">• Zero fluoride and zero sugar: This toothpaste does not contain any fluoride or sugar, making it safe for your baby\'s oral health.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">• Safe to swallow: Since babies tend to swallow toothpaste while brushing, Meril Baby Gel Toothpaste is designed to be safe if ingested.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">• Suitable for baby\'s delicate milk teeth: The formulation of this toothpaste is specifically created to cater to the delicate nature of your baby\'s milk teeth.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-07-30 23:35:23', '2026-01-14 18:12:23'),
(267, 'Parachute Just for Baby Toothpaste (Mix Fruit)', 'parachute-just-for-baby-toothpaste-mix-fruit-', '45 gm', 70, 75, 1, 6, 5, '1627673972-image-Parachute Just For Baby - Baby Toothpaste (Mix Fruit) 45 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Parachute Just for BabyTM Baby toothpaste is specially formulated for Baby teeth. Its fluoride free formula is gentle on baby’s teeth and gums. It is carefully formulated with food grade ingredients, making it safe if accidentally swallowed. Its sweet flavor is especially suited for babies and is sure to make brushing a fun experience for them</p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Benefits:</p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">1. Synthetic color free</p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">2. Fluoride Free</p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">3. Sugar Free</p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-6\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">4. SLS Free</p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-7\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">5. Australian Certified Toxic Free</p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-8\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">6. Made Safe Certified</p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">7. Gentle on Teeth and Gums</p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-10\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">8. Tested under dentist supervision</p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-11\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-12\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Ingredients:</p><p data-reactid=\".dgm1v2aaz2.6.2.0.0.0.0.2.5.1.0:$p23605.4.0.1.0.1.4.$line-13\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;segoe ui&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;droid sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Dicalcium phosphate dihydrate, a