(480, 'Pran Mixed Pickle', 'pran-mixed-pickle', '400 gm', 190, 200, 1, 5, 5, '1768747983-image-Pran Mixed Pickle 400 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">PRAN Mixed Pickle 400g is a flavorful blend of assorted vegetables and fruits, including mangoes, limes, and carrots, seasoned with a rich mix of traditional spices. This tangy and spicy condiment enhances the taste of various dishes, providing a delightful contrast to rice, bread, and curries. Packaged in a 400g glass jar, it ensures freshness and easy storage. Produced by PRAN Agro Ltd. in Bangladesh.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-05 00:09:50', '2026-01-19 01:53:03'),
