(531, 'Posto Dana (Poppy Seed )', 'posto-dana-poppy-seed-', '10 gm', 40, 50, 1, 20, 2, '1628455955-image-Posto Dana (Poppy Seed ) 50 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Poppy Seeds are small, round seeds harvested from the opium poppy plant. These seeds are commonly used in cooking for their subtle, nutty flavor and crunchy texture. Poppy seeds are often incorporated into curries, sauces, salads, and sweets.. They can also be ground into a paste to be used in various dishes.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-09 00:52:35', '2026-01-21 01:25:56'),
