(705, 'Kolson Laccha Shemai', 'kolson-laccha-shemai-', '180 gm', 48, 50, 1, 4, 2, '1628889825-image-Kolson Laccha Shemai 200 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Kolson Special Lascha Semai is a fine, delicate vermicelli perfect for making traditional desserts like Shemai or Payesh. Its soft texture cooks quickly and blends beautifully with milk, sugar, and cardamom. Ideal for special occasions or everyday indulgence. Enjoy the rich taste of tradition.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-14 01:23:45', '2026-02-02 18:01:14'),
