(817, 'Aarong Dairy UHT Mango Drink', 'aarong-dairy-uht-mango-drink', '200 ml', 34, 35, 1, 2, 1, '1629068981-image-Aarong Dairy UHT Mango Drink 200 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p data-reactid=\".29r7b0igmmo.$30876.0.1.0.1.4.$line-2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Aarong Dairy Mango Milk Drink is a delicious and refreshing beverage that combines the rich taste of mango with the creaminess of cow milk. This UHT (Ultra-High Temperature) treated drink ensures freshness and longevity, making it ideal for on-the-go consumption. It is a perfect blend for a quick, nutritious snack.</p><p data-reactid=\".29r7b0igmmo.$30876.0.1.0.1.4.$line-3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p data-reactid=\".29r7b0igmmo.$30876.0.1.0.1.4.$line-4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Usage: Consume chilled for the best taste and refreshment. Ideal for a quick drink at any time of the day.</p>', 0, 3, '2021-08-16 03:09:41', '2026-02-08 19:07:20'),
(818, 'Pepsi', 'pepsis-2-ltr', '2 ltr', 130, 130, 1, NULL, 2, '1629146640-image-Pepsi Pet 2 ltr-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Pepsi 2 ltr is a classic and delicious carbonated soft drink. The drink has a crisp and refreshing taste that is achieved through the perfect balance of sweet and tangy flavors. It\'s made with high-quality ingredients and contains no artificial preservatives or flavors.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-17 00:44:00', '2026-02-11 16:55:19'),
(819, 'Pepsi Diet', 'pepsi-diet-500-ml', '500 ml', 50, 50, 1, NULL, 1, '1629146779-image-Pepsi Diet Pet 500 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Great taste, crisp and refreshing. Zero calories. 1L / 33oz - Great for sharing with friends or when you want to save some for later!</span></p>', 0, 3, '2021-08-17 00:46:19', '2026-02-11 16:53:18'),
(820, 'Coca-Cola', 'coca-cola-500-ml', '500 ml', 50, 50, 1, NULL, 1, '1629146928-image-Coca-Cola 500 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p data-reactid=\".2fpmk6bqgcs.$2179.0.1.0.1.4.$line-0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Highlights: ORIGINAL FLAVOUR: Enjoy the deliciously refreshing original cola flavour of Coca-Cola BEST ENJOYED ICE-COLD: Enjoy this soft drink ice-cold for maximum refreshment YOUR MEAL PARTNER: Make meals tastier with a combo of your favourite dish and a chilled glass of Coke SHARE A COKE: Enjoy the real magic of everyday moments and share this cold drink with family &amp; friends ANYTIME &amp; ANYWHERE: Enjoy Coca-Cola’s crisp, delicious taste anytime with meals, at parties, or family gatherings RECYCLABLE BOTTLES: Coca-Cola comes in recyclable bottle packaging Description: Happiness is about creating Real Magic from everyday moments, turning up the energy during an afternoon lull, during those hot and long exhausting days with the crisp, delicious taste of Coca-Cola Original. Make your meals tastier &amp; share a Coke ice-cold for maximum refreshment. Enjoy this carbonated soft drink while playing fun games, binge-watching your favourite series, listening to your favourite songs and making the most of your break moments. The oh-so refreshing fizz and original taste of Coca-Cola soft drink make life’s special moments a little more special.</p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-17 00:48:48', '2026-02-11 16:29:08'),
(821, 'RC Cola', 'rc-cola', '250 ml', 20, 20, 1, NULL, 1, '1770793522-image-RC Cola 250 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">RC Cola is a carbonated beverage that is typically sold in a pet 250 ml bottle. It is a cola-flavored soda that offers a refreshing and fizzy drink option. Cola beverages are known for their sweet and slightly tangy taste.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-17 00:51:41', '2026-02-11 18:05:22'),
