(824, '7 Up', '7-up-1-ltr', '1 ltr', 80, 80, 1, NULL, 1, '1629147632-image-7 Up Pet 1 ltr-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">7 Up is a refreshing and crisp lemon-lime flavored soda that is sold in a 1 liter bottle. It is a carbonated soft drink that is known for its distinct flavor and bubbly effervescence. Made with natural lemon and lime flavors, 7 Up is caffeine-free and contains no artificial colors or flavors. Its crisp, clean taste makes it a popular choice for quenching thirst and satisfying cravings</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-17 01:00:32', '2026-02-10 19:25:46'),
(825, 'Sprite', 'sprite-500-ml', '500 ml', 50, 50, 1, NULL, 1, '1629147861-image-Sprite 500 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Highlights: REFRESHING TASTE: Open a bottle of Sprite and have a refreshing sip of this soft drink packed with the deliciousness of lemon &amp; lime. NO ADDED COLOUR: This flavoured soft drink is a clear carbonated soft drink and contains no added colours in it ULTIMATE FIZZ: Release your stress with a chilled glass of the fizzy Sprite soft drink RECYCLABLE BOTTLES: Sprite comes in recyclable bottle packaging. Description: Refreshing people since 1999, Sprite will quench your thirst, leaving you feeling refreshed. Sprite strongly believes in removing all the unnecessary stress from your life so that you can chill for real. Enjoy the flavour of lemon &amp; lime packed with the ultimate fizz in a cold glass of Sprite. Have a chilled glass of this flavoured soft drink and reset, refresh &amp; break the monotony of everyday life stress. Be it summer or winter, charge your body with the crisp &amp; cool taste of Sprite soft drink.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-17 01:04:21', '2026-02-10 19:11:07');
