(827, 'RC Q Lemon', 'rc-q-lemon-250-ml', '250 ml', 24, 25, 1, 4, 1, '1770793183-image-RC Q Lemon Pet-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">RC Q Lemon Pet 250 ml is a refreshing lemon-flavored beverage that offers a zesty burst of flavor in every sip. Perfectly carbonated, it provides a crisp and invigorating taste, making it an ideal choice for quenching your thirst on hot days or during meals. Enjoy the delightful blend of citrus and effervescence with RC Q Lemon.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-17 01:09:34', '2026-02-11 17:59:43'),
