(856, 'Pepsi', 'pepsi-250-ml-', '250 ml', 20, 20, 1, NULL, 1, '1629278412-image-Pepsi 250 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p data-reactid=\".2fpmk6bqgcs.$7859.0.1.0.1.4.$line-0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Through the years, Pepsi has evolved from being a cola drink to a brand that stands firmly for all ages.</p><p data-reactid=\".2fpmk6bqgcs.$7859.0.1.0.1.4.$line-1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Pepsi is a very popular drink for everyone. Pepsi can refresh your body and keep active.</p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-18 13:20:12', '2026-02-11 16:37:13'),
(857, 'Coca-Cola', 'coca-cola-250-ml', '250 ml', 25, 25, 1, NULL, 1, '1629278599-image-Coca-Cola 250 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Coca-Cola Original Taste Soft Drink PET Bottle 250ML. Highlights: ORIGINAL FLAVOUR: Enjoy the deliciously refreshing original cola flavour of Coca-Cola BEST ENJOYED ICE-COLD: Enjoy this soft drink ice-cold for maximum refreshment YOUR MEAL PARTNER: Make meals tastier with a combo of your favourite dish and a chilled glass of Coke SHARE A COKE: Enjoy the real magic of everyday moments and share this cold drink with family &amp; friends ANYTIME &amp; ANYWHERE: Enjoy Coca-Cola’s crisp, delicious taste anytime with meals, at parties, or family gatherings RECYCLABLE BOTTLES: Coca-Cola comes in recyclable bottle packaging Description: Happiness is about creating Real Magic from everyday moments, turning up the energy during an afternoon lull, during those hot and long exhausting days with the crisp, delicious taste of Coca-Cola Original. Make your meals tastier &amp; share a Coke ice-cold for maximum refreshment. Enjoy this carbonated soft drink while playing fun games, binge-watching your favourite series, listening to your favourite songs and making the most of your break moments. The oh-so refreshing fizz and original taste of Coca-Cola soft drink make life’s special moments a little more special.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-18 13:23:19', '2026-02-11 16:21:37'),
(858, '7 Up', '7-up-250-ml', '250 ml', 25, 25, 1, NULL, 1, '1770711773-image-7 Up 250 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Refreshingly Original. Caffeine-free with natural flavors for a crisp, clean, refreshing taste. Ingredients- Filtered Carbonated Water, High Fructose, Corn Syrup, Citric Acid, Potassium Citrate, Natural Flavors, Calcium Disodium Edta.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-18 13:25:57', '2026-02-10 19:22:53'),
(859, 'Sprite', 'sprite-250-ml', '250 ml', 25, 25, 1, NULL, 1, '1629278933-image-Sprite 250 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Highlights: REFRESHING TASTE: Open a bottle of Sprite and have a refreshing sip of this soft drink packed with the deliciousness of lemon &amp; lime NO ADDED COLOUR: This flavoured soft drink is a clear carbonated soft drink and contains no added colours in it ULTIMATE FIZZ: Release your stress with a chilled glass of the fizzy Sprite soft drink RECYCLABLE BOTTLES: Sprite comes in recyclable bottle packaging. Description: Refreshing people since 1999, Sprite will quench your thirst, leaving you feeling refreshed. Sprite strongly believes in removing all the unnecessary stress from your life so that you can chill for real. Enjoy the flavour of lemon &amp; lime packed with the ultimate fizz in a cold glass of Sprite. Have a chilled glass of this flavoured soft drink and reset, refresh &amp; break the monotony of everyday life stress. Be it summer or winter, charge your body with the crisp &amp; cool taste of Sprite soft drink.</font></span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-18 13:28:53', '2026-02-10 19:06:24'),
(860, 'Mountain Dew', 'mountain-dew-500-ml', '500 ml', 50, 50, 1, NULL, 1, '1770710081-image-Mountain Dew 500 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Mountain Dew is a carbonated soft drink with a citrus flavor that comes in a 500 ml bottle. It is a refreshing beverage that is perfect for quenching thirst and providing an energy boost. The drink is made with natural and artificial flavors, high fructose corn syrup, caffeine, and a blend of concentrated orange, lemon, and lime juices. Mountain Dew has a distinctive green color and a unique taste that appeals to fans of bold and bold flavors.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-18 13:31:36', '2026-02-10 18:54:41'),
(861, 'Mountain Dew', 'mountain-dew-250-ml', '250 ml', 25, 25, 1, NULL, 1, '1629279294-image-Mountain Dew 250 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Mountain Dew is a carbonated soft drink with a citrus flavor that comes in a 250 ml bottle. It is a refreshing beverage that is perfect for quenching thirst and providing an energy boost. The drink is made with natural and artificial flavors, high fructose corn syrup, caffeine, and a blend of concentrated orange, lemon, and lime juices. Mountain Dew has a distinctive green color and a unique taste that appeals to fans of bold and bold flavors.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-18 13:34:54', '2026-02-10 18:51:48'),
(862, 'Fanta', 'fanta-250-ml', '250 ml', 25, 25, 1, NULL, 1, '1770709225-image-Fanta 250 ml-compressed.jpg', '<div class=\"product_description\" style=\"color: rgb(104, 113, 136); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><div class=\"pr_desc\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"><p data-reactid=\".1sooyabkkww.$2219.0.1.0.1.4.$line-1\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">ADDED ORANGE FLAVOUR: FANTA soft drink is now more orangey with added orange flavour</p><p data-reactid=\".1sooyabkkww.$2219.0.1.0.1.4.$line-2\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">REFRESHING TASTE: Set your spirits free with the refreshing &amp; tingling bubbles of this soft drink</p><p data-reactid=\".1sooyabkkww.$2219.0.1.0.1.4.$line-3\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 28px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">ENJOY LIFE: Make those dull moments bright &amp; refreshing with this vibrant orange-flavoured soft drink.</p></div></div>', 1, 3, '2021-08-18 13:39:05', '2026-02-10 18:40:25'),
(863, 'Mirinda', 'mirinda', '250 ml', 25, 25, 1, NULL, 1, '1770621817-image-Mirinda 250 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Mirinda Orange is a carbonated soft drink that has a sweet and tangy orange flavor. It is made with high-quality ingredients, including carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, natural and artificial flavors, citric acid, sodium benzoate, and caffeine. Mirinda Orange is known for its bright orange color and refreshing taste, making it a popular choice for people of all ages.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-18 13:42:03', '2026-02-09 18:23:37'),
(864, 'Clemon', 'clemon-250-ml', '250 ml', 20, 20, 1, NULL, 1, '1770707412-image-Clemon 250 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">It is a good lemon-flavored drink. Having it makes you refreshed—Must-have as your companion for parties, traveling, and any time of the day.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-18 13:44:09', '2026-02-10 18:10:12'),
