(871, 'Mum Drinking Water', 'mum-drinking-water-2-ltr', '2 ltr', 40, 45, 1, 11, 2, '1629321267-image-Mum Drinking Water 2 ltr-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">MUM is a pure natural mineral drinking water. People have trust in MUM because, MUM strictly follows the guidelines &amp; standard specifications of quality level of WHO, IBWA, ICDDRB, Food and Nutrition Dept. of DU.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-19 01:14:27', '2026-02-11 18:34:02'),
