\"Aer\", a tad bit differently. That\'s the little difference we intend to make to your life, your car, and your home. No, we won\'t change your future, your world, or your boss. All we can do is to make your car, home and you feel nice. Now quickly add Aer to your dictionary, take a deep breath, and smile.</p>', 0, 3, '2021-08-21 12:01:53', '2026-02-12 18:58:24'),
