(986, 'Harpic All-In-One Toilet & Bathroom Cleaning Powder', 'harpic-all-in-one-toilet-bathroom-cleaning-powder', '400 gm', 100, 105, 1, 4, 1, '1772008242-image-Harpic All-In-One Toilet & Bathroom Cleaning Powder 400 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$39243.0.1.0.1.4.$line-1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">• All-in-1 Toilet &amp; Bathroom Cleaning Expert</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$39243.0.1.0.1.4.$line-2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">• Powder cleaner for toilet &amp; bathroom cleaning on pan, commode, basin, shower, bathroom/toilet floor</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$39243.0.1.0.1.4.$line-3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">• Gives 3 times more cleaning than regular detergent as per lab test</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$39243.0.1.0.1.4.$line-4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">• Superior blue speckles formula to produce cleaning foam</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$39243.0.1.0.1.4.$line-5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">• Cleaning foam removes tough bathroom &amp; toilet stains</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$39243.0.1.0.1.4.$line-6\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">• Kills 99.9% of germs</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$39243.0.1.0.1.4.$line-7\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">• Malodor Control Technology prevents the bad odors of toilets</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$39243.0.1.0.1.4.$line-8\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Description</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$39243.0.1.0.1.4.$line-9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Key Features: Harpic All-in-1 Toilet &amp; Bathroom Cleaning Powder is a specialized product, which is the ultimate one-stop solution for all your toilet &amp; bathroom cleaning needs. Unlike re