(1001, 'Harpic Bathroom Cleaning Liquid Rose', 'harpic-bathroom-cleaning-liquid-rose', '500 ml', 135, 140, 1, 3, 2, '1772007949-image-Harpic Bathroom Cleaning Liquid Rose 500 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Multipurpose Surface Bathroom Cleaner (Floor, Basin &amp; Tiles) Removes tough stains Kills 99.9% of germs Gives a sparkling clean shine to the bathroom surface Description: Harpic Bathroom Cleaning Liquid Rose 500ml is a strong bathroom disinfectant and cleaning liquid that helps remove the toughest of stains. Harpic Bathroom Cleaner can be used as a tile cleaner, basin cleaner, or even for floor cleaning in the bathroom area. It also removes 99.9% of germs and gives your bathroom a pleasant fresh fragrance. Usage Information: Dilute 1.5 capful in half a bucket of water (4 Liters), apply on the surface, leave for 5mins and then scrub gently. Lastly, rinse with water. Use undiluted for tough stains by putting the liquid directly on the stain/scrubber, scrub gently &amp; rinse through. Safety Measure: Always use Harpic separately. Do not mix with other products. This product is not edible and harmful to eyes and skin. Wash with water immediately in case of contact with Skin or Eyes and consult a doctor. Read the label for details. About the Manufacturer: Harpic is a registered Trademark of Reckitt PLC headquartered in England. The first Harpic product was manufactured during the 1920s in England. Harpic products are made in Bangladesh by Reckitt (Bangladesh) PLC.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-23 11:04:45', '2026-02-25 19:25:49'),
(1002, 'Mr. Brasso Glass & Multisurface Cleaner Refill', 'mr-brasso-glass-multisurface-cleaner-refill', '500 ml', 185, 190, 1, 2, 5, '1772007692-image-Mr-compressed (1).jpg', '<p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$36813.0.1.0.1.4.$line-0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">●Glass &amp; Multisurface Cleaner: Can be used in glass, metal, plastic, laminates and other appliances for cleaning efficiently</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$36813.0.1.0.1.4.$line-1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">●Item Weight: 500 ml; available in Spray Gun &amp; Refill Pack, 5Litre; available in Refill Pack</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$36813.0.1.0.1.4.$line-2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Description</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$36813.0.1.0.1.4.$line-3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Mr. Brasso Glass and Multisurface Cleaner cleans the surface of your Television &amp; other electronic appliances, Computers, Window glasses, Mirrors, table tops, Fridge &amp; Kitchen appliances, Vehicle windshields, and Laminated furniture.</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$36813.0.1.0.1.4.$line-4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Usage Information: While using Mr. Brasso Refill Pack, replace the bottle cap with an old spray gun. Read the label for more details.</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$36813.0.1.0.1.4.$line-5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Safety Measure: Unplug electronic appliances before cleaning with Mr. Brasso. Wash eyes with water immediately in case of contact with eyes while spraying. Read the label for details.</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$36813.0.1.0.1.4.$line-6\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">About the Manufacturer: Mr. Brasso is a brand of Reckitt Benckiser Bangladesh Limited which is manufactured in Bangladesh.</p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-23 11:14:59', '2026-02-25 19:21:32');
