(1004, 'Lizol Disinfectant Surface & Floor Cleaner Lavender', 'lizol-disinfectant-surface-floor-cleaner-lavender-500-ml', '500 ml', 155, 160, 1, 3, 2, '1772006472-image-Lizol Disinfectant Surface & Floor Cleaner Lavender 500 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$7631.0.1.0.1.4.$line-1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Disinfectant Surface Cleaner: Removes powerful stains &amp; kills 99.9% of germs on all surfaces</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$7631.0.1.0.1.4.$line-2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Use directly or diluted for regular use, Suitable for cleaning all kinds of surfaces.</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$7631.0.1.0.1.4.$line-3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Leaves a Pleasant Fragrance. Maximum Shelf Life Months 24</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.$7631.0.1.0.1.4.$line-4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Available Variants: Floral, Citrus, Jasmine, Lavender; Available Sizes: 500ml, 975ml &amp; 5L</p><p data-reactid=\".22s2s8ggvme.