(1021, 'Harpic Flushmatic In-Cistern Toilet Cleaner', 'harpic-flushmatic-in-cistern-toilet-cleaner', '50 gm', 160, 165, 1, 3, 5, '1771967516-image-Harpic Flushmatic Marine In-Cistern Toilet Cleaner Block 50 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p data-reactid=\".sihgod7lro.$9064.0.1.0.1.4.$line-2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Harpic Flushmatic Toilet Cleaning In-Cistern Block is a drop-in tank tablet which can be used for any accessible cistern. It works by creating strong foam every time you flush the toilet, which helps to maintain the cleanliness &amp; freshness in the toilet bowl.</p><p data-reactid=\".sihgod7lro.$9064.0.1.0.1.4.$line-3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p data-reactid=\".sihgod7lro.$9064.0.1.0.1.4.$line-4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Usage Direction: 1. Open It - Remove the block from the packet. Do not remove the plastic covering. 2. Drop It - Drop the block into the cistern/tank but away from the water inlet. 3. Flush It - To activate, wait for 10 minutes before the first flush. 4. Forget It - Replace the block when the color disappears.</p>', 1, 3, '2021-08-23 12:34:49', '2026-02-25 08:11:56'),
