(1298, 'Pond\'s Face Wash Bright Beauty', 'pond-s-face-wash-bright-beauty', '100 gm', 200, 210, 1, 4, 5, '1773471876-image-Pond\'s Face Wash Bright Beauty 100 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Is your true complexion lost or hidden? Over time dead skin cells accumulate on your skin, hiding your true complexion, and making you look dull and dark. New and improved Pond\'s White Beauty Face Wash. 1st ever facewash with Double Brightening Action to renew your complexion every day. Now get the clinically proven benefits with Pond\'s. Your complexion is hidden under layers of dead skin cells and pollution. Pond’s White Beauty Face Wash with advanced vitamin B3+ formula will cleanse your skin and give you a spotless glow. It goes deep to clean dead skin cells and uncovers millions of new cells- so that you can get your hidden complexion back. Infused with vitamin B3+, it removes layers of dead skin cells and strengthens the skin\'s natural renewal process, revealing new bright cells. Renew your complexion with everyday wash. Clinically proven to give you a glow from the first wash. Its double brightness action wipes out dead skin cells so that you can say goodbye to skin dullness. This helps bring out the complexion locked inside which shows clearly after every use of Pond\'s White Beauty Facewash. This is truly your solution to spotless and glowing skin.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-09-18 10:00:14', '2026-03-14 17:04:36'),
(1299, 'Himalaya Purifying Neem Face Wash', 'himalaya-purifying-neem-face-washs-150-ml', '150 ml', 190, 225, 1, 15, 5, '1631945010-image-Himalaya Purifying Neem Face Wash 150 ml-compressed.jpg', NULL, 0, 3, '2021-09-18 10:03:30', '2026-03-14 17:00:02'),
(1300, 'Himalaya Purifying Neem Face Wash', 'himalaya-purifying-neem-face-wash-100-ml', '100 ml', 200, 230, 1, 13, 5, '1773471155-image-Himalaya Purifying Neem Face Wash 100 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">The Himalaya drugs Ltd. Clinically Proven Pimple-free Healthy Skin Expert Himalaya\'s Purifying Neem Face Wash is a soap-free formulation that cleans impurities and helps clear pimples. Ingredients: Neem Neem is an excellent skincare ingredient known for its antibacterial properties. It improves general skin health and combating bacterial infection like acne. Turmeric Turmeric has been used as an antiseptic for centuries and is regarded as one of nature\'s most powerful healers. The herb helps to even out your skin tone and color, making it an excellent ingredient in a face wash. Turmeric has strong anti-inflammatory properties, which help soothe your skin.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-09-18 10:12:55', '2026-03-14 16:52:35'),
(1301, 'Himalaya Purifying Neem Face Wash', 'himalaya-purifying-neem-face-wash', '50 ml', 115, 130, 1, 11, 5, '1773471298-image-Himalaya Purifying Neem Face Wash 50 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Himalaya\'s Purifying Neem Facewash is a soap-free formulation that cleans impurities and helps clear pimples. A natural blend of Neem and Turmeric are known for their antimicrobial properties, to help combat and prevent the recurrence of pimples over time.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-09-18 10:15:59', '2026-03-14 17:00:54'),
(1302, 'Ponds Face Wash Pure White', 'ponds-face-wash-pure-white', '100 gm', 195, 200, 1, 2, 5, '1631945984-image-Ponds Face Wash Pure White 100 gm-compressed.jpg', NULL, 0, 3, '2021-09-18 10:19:44', '2026-03-16 16:30:07'),
(1303, 'Ponds Face Wash Scrub', 'ponds-face-wash-scrub', '100 gm', 160, 165, 1, 3, 5, '1631946199-image-Ponds Face Wash Scrub 100 gm-compressed.jpg', NULL, 0, 3, '2021-09-18 10:23:19', '2026-03-16 16:29:44'),
(1304, 'Pond\'s Bright Beauty Cream (Imported)', 'pond-s-bright-beauty-cream-imported-35-gm', '35 gm', 250, 280, 1, 10, 5, '1773818811-image-Pond\'s Bright Beauty Cream (Imported) 35gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 69, 79); font-family: Montserrat;\">Make your skin look its best with Pond\'s White Beauty Fairness Cream. This cream is designed to provide you multifaceted benefits. It not only makes your skin look lighter but also reduces dark spots. You can make your skin look radiant and bright with the regular use of this cream that is has SPF 15 to protect the skin against the harmful effects of UV rays. Now, you can nourish and protect your skin at the same time. This cream is suitable for daily use as it is effective yet gentle. Get your dream skin in a convenient way with the help of Pond\'s White Beauty Fairness Cream.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-09-18 10:27:27', '2026-03-18 17:26:51'),
(1305, 'Fair And Lovely  Advanced MultivitaminFairness Cream', 'fair-and-lovely-advanced-multivitaminfairness-cream', '50 gm', 120, 125, 1, 4, 5, '1631997157-image-Fair And Lovely  Advanced MultivitaminFairness Cream 50 gm-compressed.jpg', NULL, 1, 3, '2021-09-19 00:32:37', '2022-09-11 17:15:23'),
(1306, 'White Tone Face Powder', 'white-tone-face-powder-30-gm', '30 gm', 160, 200, 1, 20, 5, '1774286978-image-White Tone Face Powder 30 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Discover the secret to a flawless and radiant complexion with White Tone Face Powder. This 50 gm compact powder is designed to enhance your skin\'s natural beauty, giving you a brighter, even-toned, and youthful appearance. Whether you\'re looking to set your makeup or simply want to freshen up your skin throughout the day, White Tone Face Powder is your go-to beauty essential.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-09-19 00:36:10', '2026-03-24 03:29:38'),
