(1751, 'Emami Fair And Handsome Fairness Cream', 'emami-fair-and-handsome-fairness-cream-30-gm', '30 gm', 190, 200, 1, 5, 5, '1773816517-image-Emami Fair And Handsome Fairness Cream 30 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p data-reactid=\".s3bxy7twaa.i.2.0.0.0.0.0.1.1.0.0.1.4.$line-2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Emami Fair And Handsome Fairness Cream (30 gm) is a skincare product formulated to provide a brighter, more even complexion for men. It\'s marketed as a fairness cream that also helps to reduce dark spots, even skin tone, and provide a fresh, radiant appearance.</p><p data-reactid=\".s3bxy7twaa.i.2.0.0.0.0.0.1.1.0.0.1.4.$line-3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p data-reactid=\".s3bxy7twaa.i.2.0.0.0.0.0.1.1.0.0.1.4.$line-4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Ingredients:</p><p data-reactid=\".s3bxy7twaa.i.2.0.0.0.0.0.1.1.0.0.1.4.$line-5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Vitamin E: Helps nourish the skin and protect it from environmental damage.</p><p data-reactid=\".s3bxy7twaa.i.2.0.0.0.0.0.1.1.0.0.1.4.$line-6\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Licorice Extract: Known for its skin-lightening properties, helping to reduce dark spots and even out skin tone.</p><p data-reactid=\".s3bxy7twaa.i.2.0.0.0.0.0.1.1.0.0.1.4.$line-7\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Glycerin: Moisturizes the skin, keeping it soft and hydrated​.</p><p data-reactid=\".s3bxy7twaa.i.2.0.0.0.0.0.1.1.0.0.1.4.$line-8\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\"></p><p data-reactid=\".s3bxy7twaa.i.2.0.0.0.0.0.1.1.0.0.1.4.$line-9\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Use: Emami Fair and Handsome Fairness Cream is designed for daily use. It can be applied to clean, dry skin, typically after washing the face. It helps to lighten skin over time, giving a more uniform complexion and improving skin radiance. This cream is also formulated to prevent oil buildup, making it suitable for oily skin as well​.</p>', 1, 3, '2021-10-20 03:11:11', '2026-03-18 16:48:37'),
