saction=\"\" jscontroller=\"zYmgkd\" jsuid=\"b962ge_11\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-complete=\"true\" style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Intense Oil Control</span>: Effectively removes excess sebum and oils without stripping the skin of its essential moisture, ensuring an oil-free feel all day.</span></li><li class=\"dF3vjf\" jsaction=\"\" jscontroller=\"vsuOFb\" jsuid=\"b962ge_12\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-hveid=\"CAQQAg\" data-complete=\"true\" data-sae=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc; padding-inline-start: 4px;\"><span class=\"T286Pc\" data-sfc-cp=\"\" jsaction=\"\" jscontroller=\"fly6D\" jsuid=\"b962ge_13\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-complete=\"true\" aria-owns=\"action-menu-parent-container\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span class=\"Yjhzub\" jsaction=\"\" jscontroller=\"zYmgkd\" jsuid=\"b962ge_14\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-complete=\"true\" style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Icy Cooling Sensation</span>: Infused with&nbsp;<span class=\"Yjhzub\" jsaction=\"\" jscontroller=\"zYmgkd\" jsuid=\"b962ge_15\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-complete=\"true\" style=\"font-weight: 700;\">menthol</span>, it provides an immediate cooling and refreshing effect, making it ideal for a morning wake-up or post-workout routine.</span></li></ul>', 1, 3, '2021-10-21 02:39:37', '2026-03-16 16:54:50'),
