(2012, 'Glow & Lovely Face Cream Blemish Balm', 'glow-lovely-face-cream-blemish-balms-18-gm', '18 gm', 155, 165, 1, 6, 5, '1773815407-image-Glow & Lovely Face Cream Blemish Balm 18gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(46, 49, 56); white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Glow &amp; Lovely (formerly Fair &amp; Lovely) BB Cream for all skin types, with Multivitamins and a hint of Foundation for a makeup like Glow. Feel more confident in your own skin with the new Glow &amp; Lovely (formerly Fair &amp; Lovely) BB Cream. This cream blends in perfectly to give you a Makeup like Glow every day. It is enriched with multivitamins that work from deep within to nourish your skin, foundation blends in and covers dark spots and blemishes to give you an even skin tone. Use it daily to hide dark spots and blemishes and achieve a bright, even-toned look every day. SPF 15 keeps your glow protected in the sun, and matte texture leaves your face feeling non-oily and fresh throughout the day. The Glow &amp; Lovely BB Cream is easy to apply and gives instant results: Just dot the cream across cleansed face and neck and spread evenly using fingertips to get a make-up finish in seconds! Glow &amp; Lovely BB Cream makes you look perfect instantly. So now you have the answer to get the perfect make-up finish for any occasion, be it your first day of college to first interview, an office party or any festive occasion. Now, Makeup like Glow is super easy only with the Glow &amp; Lovely BB Cream!</font></span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-10-23 03:30:21', '2026-03-18 16:30:07'),
