(2047, 'YC Lemon Extract Whitening Face Wash', 'yc-lemon-extract-whitening-face-wash-100-ml', '100 ml', 400, 510, 1, 21, 5, '1634951620-image-YC Lemon Extract Whitening Face Wash 100 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Face wash, specially formulated to provide deep cleansing for your skin by totally eliminating pore blocking residues. Lemon natural extracts help controlling excess oil. It reveals skin smooth radiant, clear, moist and fresh.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-10-23 05:13:40', '2026-03-16 16:08:23'),
(2048, 'YC Milk Extract Whitening Face Wash', 'yc-milk-extract-whitening-face-wash', '100 ml', 400, 510, 1, 21, 5, '1634951751-image-YC Milk Extract Whitening Face Wash 100 ml-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(46, 49, 56); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">YC Face Wash with Milk Extract is a skincare product that typically comes in a 100ml size. It is formulated to cleanse and nourish the skin, leaving it soft, hydrated, and refreshed. The milk extract in the face wash is known for its moisturizing properties and is often included to help maintain the skin\'s natural moisture balance.YC Whitening Face Wash Milk Extract is effective to remove grime, dust, and sweat from your face. It also unclogs pores to minimize their appearance. Use this regularly for skin that is clean, healthy and bright.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-10-23 05:15:51', '2026-03-16 16:15:24'),
(2049, 'Himalaya Oil Clear Face Wash Strawberry', 'himalaya-oil-clear-face-wash-strawberry', '100 ml', 140, 150, 1, 6, 5, '1634952445-image-Himalaya Oil Clear Face Wash Strawberry 100 ml-compressed.jpg', NULL, 0, 3, '2021-10-23 05:19:17', '2024-11-20 13:17:37'),
(2050, 'Himalaya Oil Clear Face Wash Blueberry', 'himalaya-oil-clear-face-wash-blueberry', '100 ml', 190, 199, 1, 4, 10, '1634952287-image-Himalaya Oil Clear Face Wash Blueberry 100 ml-compressed.jpg', NULL, 0, 3, '2021-10-23 05:24:47', '2026-01-05 16:45:58'),
(2051, 'Glow & Lovely Facewash Bright Glow', 'glow-lovely-facewash-bright-glow', '50 gm', 80, 85, 1, 5, 1, '1773642453-image-Glow & Lovely Instaglow Facewash with Multivitamins  50 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Presenting Glow &amp; Lovely Instaglow face wash (Formerly known as Fair &amp; Lovely) Enriched with multivitamins like Vitamin B3, C &amp; E, to give you an instant glow. Deep* cleanses to remove dirt and pollution from deep* within your skin with every wash. Exfoliates to remove dead skin cells and helps remove germs to unclog pores with every wash. Washes away skin impurities and boosts skin defence. The facewash effectively cleanses your skin to give you an instant glow. Specially formulated with glycerine, myristic acids, and enriched with multivitamins, the face wash ensures a bright glowing clear skin. Its benefits are: 1. Clear brighter face 2. Clean instant Glow 3. Soft and smoother feel for a healthy look 4. Boosts skin defence. It is specially formulated to suit all skin types. The Glow &amp; Lovely has been evaluated in clinical and consumer tests for the claimed benefits with excellent results that have been certified and endorsed by internationally renowned dermatologists. For best results, use twice a day in the morning and evening. For a good skin care regime use Glow &amp; Lovely Advanced Multivitamin Face Cream afterwards.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-10-23 05:32:07', '2026-03-16 16:27:33'),
