(2120, 'Meril Baby Powder', 'meril-baby-powder', '100 gm', 130, 140, 1, 7, 5, '1730002475-image-Meril Baby Powder 100 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">Meril Baby Powder is formulated with a triple action formula that provides comprehensive protection against rash, skin irritation, and prickly heat. Designed to keep your baby comfortable and happy, especially during the hot summer months, our baby powder is a must-have for every parent. With its gentle and effective formula, it helps to maintain the health and well-being of your little one\'s delicate skin.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">• Helps to absorb excess moisture, keeping your baby\'s skin dry and free from discomfort.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">• Helps to calm irritated skin and promote healthy skin renewal.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">• Preventing friction and irritation on your baby\'s delicate skin.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">• Helps to soothe and protect the skin from rashes and redness.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 69, 70); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;\">• Gentle and pleasing fragrance to enhance your baby\'s experience and leave them feeling fresh.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-10-24 02:56:57', '2026-01-13 17:32:14'),
