(2584, 'Aarong Dairy UHT Chocolate Milk', 'aarong-dairy-uht-chocolate-milk', '125 ml', 25, 25, 1, NULL, 1, '1635803819-image-Aarong Dairy UHT Chocolate Milk 125 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">The Aarong Dairy Chocolate Milk Drink UHT (125 ml) is a ready-to-drink beverage made from high-quality milk and cocoa, offering a rich chocolate flavor. It is processed using Ultra-High Temperature (UHT) technology, ensuring long shelf life without the need for refrigeration until opened. This drink provides a combination of the nutritional benefits of milk with the delightful taste of chocolate, making it a popular choice for kids and adults alike. It\'s a convenient source of calcium and energy, ideal for on-the-go refreshments or a quick snack.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2021-11-02 01:56:59', '2026-02-08 19:05:59'),
