(2844, 'Sprite Mint', 'sprite-mint', '250 ml', 25, 25, 1, NULL, 1, '1770711261-image-Sprite Mint-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><font face=\"Arial\">Introducing Sprite Mint Pet 250ml – a refreshing twist on the classic lemon-lime soda you love. Infused with a burst of cool mint, this 250 ml pet bottle delivers an invigorating and crisp flavor experience. Perfect for quenching your thirst on hot days or adding a zesty kick to your favorite cocktails. Enjoy the sparkling freshness of Sprite Mint with every sip!</font></span></p>', 1, 3, '2026-02-10 19:14:21', '2026-02-10 19:14:21'),
(2845, 'Coca-Cola Diet Can', 'coca-cola-diet-can', '250 ml', 70, 70, 1, NULL, 1, '1770788109-image-Coca-Cola Can Diet-compressed.jpg', '<p data-reactid=\".2fpmk6bqgcs.$26423.0.1.0.1.4.$line-0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Highlights:</p><p data-reactid=\".2fpmk6bqgcs.$26423.0.1.0.1.4.$line-1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">ZERO SUGAR: Coca-Cola Zero comes in a new and real Coca-Cola taste without the sugar and calories BEST ENJOYED ICE-COLD: Enjoy this soft drink ice-cold for maximum refreshment IDEAL FOR CALORIE CONSCIOUS PEOPLE: This lighter cold drink is perfect for those who are calorie-conscious and want to monitor their intake YOUR MEAL PARTNER: Make meals tastier with a combo of your favourite dish and a chilled glass of Coke RECYCLABLE PACKAGING: Coca-Cola cans are recyclable, ensuring environmental sustainability. Description: Discover a connection between fun, taste, no sugar &amp; no calories with Coca-Cola Zero. This cold drink is a lighter carbonated soft drink without sugar &amp; no calories, ideal for those who are calorie-conscious and want to monitor their intake. Enjoy an ice-cold can of Coke with your meals or while playing fun games, binge-watching your favourite series, listening to your favourite songs and making the most of your break moments. The oh-so-refreshing fizz and taste of the Coca-Cola Zero soft drink make life’s special moments a little more special.</p>', 1, 3, '2026-02-11 16:35:09', '2026-02-11 16:35:09'),
