(2880, 'YC Lemon Extract Whitening Face Wash', 'yc-lemon-extract-whitening-face-wash-50-ml', '50 ml', 250, 295, 1, 15, 5, '1773641616-image-YC Lemon 50 ML-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Face wash, specially formulated to provide deep cleansing for your skin by totally eliminating pore blocking residues. Lemon natural extracts help controlling excess oil. It reveals skin smooth radiant, clear, moist and fresh.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2026-03-16 16:13:36', '2026-03-16 16:13:36'),
(2881, 'Garnier Men Turbo Bright Anti Pollution Double Action Face Wash', 'garnier-men-turbo-bright-anti-pollution-double-action-face-wash', '50 gm', 250, 280, 1, 10, 5, '1773643326-image-Garnier Men Turbo Bright Anti Pollution Double Action Face Wash 50 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">According to&nbsp;</span><font color=\"#0a0a0a\" face=\"Google Sans, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Garnier</span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">, the combination of&nbsp;</span><span class=\"Yjhzub\" jsaction=\"\" jscontroller=\"zYmgkd\" jsuid=\"zE2AHe_w\" data-sfc-cb=\"\" data-complete=\"true\" style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">black charcoal and icy clay</span><span style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;removes all traces of dust, grime, and environmental pollutants from deep within the pores.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2026-03-16 16:42:06', '2026-03-16 16:42:06'),
(2882, 'Glow & Lovely Advanced Multivitamin Cream', 'glow-lovely-advanced-multivitamin-cream-100-gm', '100 gm', 290, 300, 1, 3, 5, '1773644902-image-Glow & Lovely Advanced Multi Vitamin Cream 100 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Glow &amp; Lovely Advanced Multi Vitamin Cream (formerly known as Fair &amp; Lovely) works like a skin expert to give you a radiant glow which is skin clarity, brightness, and Radiance. Enriched with Vitamin B3, C, and E, this cream gets quickly absorbed and penetrates deep* into the skin, to brighten skin cells, reduce spots, and illuminate skin from the inside out. Vitamin B3 also known as Niacimide is known to improve the skin barrier, act as an anti-inflammatory, protect the skin’s natural health, and give a glow. Vitamin C is known to protect the skin from external damage and is known to improve skin immunity and reduce spots. Vitamin E is known to moisturize your skin from deep within keeping it hydrated. Allantoin helps remove dull skin cells from the top layers of the skin revealing soft smooth glowing skin. Also has antioxidants that help reduce dark circles. This formulation is clinically proven to give an even-toned; glowing skin which is nonoily. It has UVA &amp; UVB sunscreens known to protect the skin by blocking UV rays. The product has no bleaching agents and is dermatologically tested and proven. Just dot over the face and massage evenly over the face and neck. Use twice daily for best results after cleansing the skin.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2026-03-16 17:08:22', '2026-03-16 17:08:22'),
(2883, 'Glow & Lovely Advanced Multivitamin Cream (Imported)', 'glow-lovely-advanced-multivitamin-cream-imported-', '80 gm', 430, 450, 1, 4, 5, '1773645627-image-Glow & Lovely Advanced Multivitamin Cream 80 gm-compressed.jpg', NULL, 1, 3, '2026-03-16 17:20:27', '2026-03-16 17:20:27'),
(2884, 'Glow & Lovely Bright Serum Sunscreen UV DUO', 'glow-lovely-bright-serum-sunscreen-uv-duo-50-gm', '50 gm', 280, 300, 1, 6, 5, '1773814709-image-Glow & Lovely Bright Serum Sunscreen UV DUO SPF50 50g-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(46, 49, 56); white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><font face=\"Arial\">This larger 50g pack offers the same brightening and protective formula with SPF30. It nourishes skin with vitamins while guarding against harmful sun rays. The serum-like texture provides hydration, quick absorption, and a fresh glow. Perfect for everyday wear, indoors or outdoors, it reduces tanning while maintaining soft, radiant skin.</font></span></p>', 1, 3, '2026-03-18 16:18:29', '2026-03-18 16:18:29'),
(2885, 'Glow & Lovely Bright Serum Sunscreen UV DUO', 'glow-lovely-bright-serum-sunscreen-uv-duo-25-gm', '25 gm', 150, 160, 1, 6, 5, '1773815057-image-Glow & Lovely Bright Serum Sunscreen UV DUO 25 gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(46, 49, 56); white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Formulated with SPF50, this sunscreen provides stronger defense against sun damage while boosting brightness. It prevents tanning, hydrates the skin, and gives a healthy glow. The serum texture is fast-absorbing, non-sticky, and leaves skin fresh all day. A travel-friendly 25g size makes it perfect for daily outdoor use.</font></span></p>', 1, 3, '2026-03-18 16:24:17', '2026-03-18 16:24:17'),
(2886, 'Pond\'s Vanishing Cream', 'pond-s-vanishing-cream-50-gm', '50 gm', 85, 90, 1, 5, 2, '1773817397-image-Ponds Vanishing Cream 50gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(46, 49, 56); white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Ponds Vanishing Cream designed for oily skin. Get soft and supple skin all through the summer. This matte formula ensures oil free smooth skin.</font></span></p>', 1, 3, '2026-03-18 17:03:17', '2026-03-18 17:03:17'),
(2887, 'Lifebuoy Skin Cleansing Soap Bar Lemon Fresh', 'lifebuoy-skin-cleansing-soap-bar-lemon-fresh-90-gm', '90 gm', 54, 55, 1, 1, 1, '1773822810-image-Lifebuoy Skin Cleansing Soap Bar Lemon Fresh 90gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(46, 49, 56); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Experience a refreshing shower every day with LIFEBUOY Lemon Fresh Soap Bar. It rejuvenates your senses keeping you fresh throughout the day. Formulated with an efficient cleansing property of lemons, this soap bar is packed with natural antibacterial properties. This disinfectant soap protects your skin from disease-causing bacteria and ensures 100% better germ protection for you and your family. The citrusy fragrance will leave you thoroughly fresh.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2026-03-18 18:33:30', '2026-03-18 18:33:30'),
(2888, 'Fiama Gel+Cream Moisturising Bar With Frangipani & Almond Cream', 'fiama-gel-cream-moisturising-bar-with-frangipani-almond-cream-125gm', '125 gm', 160, 170, 1, 5, 1, '1773907199-image-Fiama Gel+Cream Moisturising Bar With Frangipani & Almond Cream 125gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space-collapse: break-spaces;\">Happy mood and cheerful skin, that is the thing that you need for an entirely decent day. Also, the Fiama Gel+ Crème range, a special formulation of gel and crème, gives you just that. It has invigorating gel, with the integrity of Frangipani to stimulate your faculties and lift your temperament, and saturating crème with the power of Almond cream, to saturate your skin and spoil it with affection and care. So whether it’s a date, a gathering, a wedding, or simply a typical day, you’ll be prepared for it, come what may.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2026-03-19 17:59:59', '2026-03-19 17:59:59'),
(2889, 'Dettol Bathing Soap Bar Skincare Mini 27 gm', 'dettol-bathing-soap-bar-skincare-mini-27-gm', '1 pcs', 15, 15, 1, NULL, 1, '1773909735-image-Dettol Bathing Soap Bar Skincare 27gm-compressed.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;lucida grande&quot;, tahoma, verdana, arial, sans-serif;\">Dettol Skincare Soap comes with a nourishing moisturizer •Dettol Skincare Soap is a Grade 1 Soap- providing the best value for your purchase. Description Dettol soap Skincare bathing bar soap is a Grade-1 soap. It comes with moisturizers. It cleanses and protects your skin for a hygienic clean and healthy, refreshing feeling every day. Be sure. Get Dettol\'s trusted protection from a wide range of unseen germs.. Available in Original, Cool, Skincare, Aloe Vera &amp; Fresh variants. Usage Information: Remove the wrapper and wet the soap, rub your palms together until the soap is bubbly, and apply soap over the entire body avoiding eye areas. Lastly, rinse yourself with water and dry up. Safety Measure: This product is not edible. Keep away from the eye area, and rinse thoroughly if contacted. Consult a doctor immediately looking into the severity of the discomfort. Read the label for details. About the Manufacturer: Dettol &amp; Sword devices are registered trademarks of Reckitt PLC. Dettol has protected health for over 80 years and is used 2 billion times each day in over 124 countries. Dettol Soaps in Bangladesh is manufactured and marketed by Reckitt Bangladesh PLC.</span></p>', 1, 3, '2026-03-19 18:42:15', '2026-03-19 18:42:15');
